## Vue Standards

- Use Composition API with `<script setup>` syntax; no Options API in new code
- Extract reusable logic into composables (`use` prefix) in a `composables/` directory
- Use `defineProps` with runtime validation; prefer typed props via `withDefaults`
- Keep components under 200 lines; split into smaller components freely
- Use `v-model` for two-way bindings; emit `update:modelValue` from child components
- Prefer `computed` over methods for derived values
- Test with Vue Test Utils and Vitest; assert on rendered output and emitted events
